data.description: Located in the center of town on the beach block! This 2 bedroom 1 bath posh condominium is sure to please the entire family. You will enjoy the centralized location. Park the car and enjoy walking to area restaurants, shops and the beach. The condo has been remodeled with newer engineered flooring, bathroom and fresh paint. The owners have kept it in tip top shape. The $145 a month condo fee is very affordable and takes care of your share of the condo building insurance and common area maintenance. There is assigned parking. Rentals are ok and pets too! This would make an excellent rental property or beach getaway. Comes furnished, turnkey and ready to go! What are you waiting for?
